                "type": "stat_block_section"
              }
            ],
            "effect": "Tokainen's chosen activates the latent magic in their brand, then launches a ball of flames with a range of 60 feet that explodes in a 10-foot burst. Creatures in the area take 6d6 fire damage (DC 22 basic Reflex save). A creature that fails their save is additionally dealt 1d4 persistent fire damage.   \nFor 1 minute, the brand's excess magic suffuses their hands, causing their fists and any weapons they wield to radiate a nimbus of fire, dealing an additional 1d10 fire damage on a Strike. While their hands radiate fire in this way, their fists lose the nonlethal trait.",
            "frequency": "once per hour",
            "links": [
              {
