            "name": "Take \u2018Em Down",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "Using their guisarme, Tokainen's chosen makes a Trip and a Strike against a target in reach. They can make these attacks in any order, but both attacks must have the same target. Their multiple attack penalty doesn't increase until after both attacks are completed.",
